<title>Configuration</title>

<para>Example <filename>nineml.properties</filename> file:</para>

<programlisting>verbose=true
pretty-print=false
ignore-trailing-whitespace=true
graphviz=/usr/local/bin/dot</programlisting>

<para>Read from <filename>.nineml.properties</filename> in the current directory,
or <filename>nineml.properties</filename> in the same directory as the CoffeePot
jar file, or from the classpath.</para>

